snippet.title: Banjo Kazooie Jiggies of Time (4/11) DEATH MOUNTAIN
snippet.description:
#BanjoKazooie #LegendOfZelda #SuperMario64
THE LEGEND OF BANJO KAZOOIE - THE JIGGIES OF TIME is a full Banjo Kazooie mod in the world of Zelda: Ocarina of Time.

SUPPORT my Youtube channel: https://www.patreon.com/Kurko or https://www.paypal.me/KurkoMods
Odysee: https://odysee.com/$/invite/@Kurko_Mods:d
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/kurko_mods
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Markus_Kurko 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/Kurko_mods/

DOWNLOAD PATCH 1.3 (UPDATED December 6th 2020) just drop your "Banjo-Kazooie (U) [!]" rom here https://patch.wedarobi.com/bk_jiggies_of_time
